Deployment Instructions:-

1. Once all the docker and docker-compose files are written, go the parent directory in terminal type "sudo docker-compose up" 

2. Then check all images by the command "sudo docker images".

3. Now login to your account and push the image in docker hub by the commands
	"docker login --username=yourhubusername --email=youremail@company.com"
	"docker tag imgeID yourhubusername/repoName:tagName"
	"docker push yourhubusername/repoName"

4. Once it is pushed, Go to the server pull and run by the following command
	"docker run --name name -p portNumber yourhubusername/repoName" 

5. Now write and start/restart your ngnix file by the command "sudo service nginx restart".
